<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Life returned to normal on Thursday as Felicity Jones returned to work just weeks after welcoming her first child.  </p>

<p>The actress, 36, was on set in Twickenham, south west London as she filmed scenes for her latest movie, forthcoming romantic drama The Last Letter from Your Lover. </p>

<p>Dressed in character as central character Ellie Haworth, she was seen shooting an outdoor scene with co-star Nabhaan Rizwan.  </p>

