<p>The British star looked focused as the pair faced one another across a small table outside a local cafe during what appeared to be a heated exchange. </p>

<p>In accordance with current health and safety guidelines, Felicity wore a protective face covering as she mingled with crew members while relaxing between scenes.</p>

<p>Evidently keen to document her latest film project, the actress was seen taking pictures of the surrounding area on her iPhone as she waited for the cameras to roll.  </p>

